explanation: [0-0] A green cartoon figure lies comfortably in a blue sink, facing rightward. Below the sink is a pipe with a showerhead underneath. Further down is a rectangular bathroom floor. On the right wall, there's a red switch, surrounded by brown patterned decoration. The upper part shows a blue background with various geometric patterns.

[0-9] Next, a black cartoon cat walks into the bathroom from the left side of the screen. The green cartoon figure swims leisurely in the blue water. The black cat presses the red button, and blue water sprays from the showerhead. It rubs its body with both hands, happily taking a shower. The water in the sink gradually decreases, and the green figure looks surprised and then jumps out of the sink, running to the left. It carries a green bucket and pours water into the sink, repeating this twice. The water in the sink increases and then decreases again. The black cat continues to shower. The green figure hasn't returned for a long time, and the water in the sink runs out. The black cat looks up in surprise and repeatedly presses the switch on the wall. The blue background with geometric patterns keeps scrolling to the right.
